{"tid":2132252,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【信奉《基本法》】我信唯一的《基本法》，全能的人大，天地萬物，無論有形無形，都是祂所創造的。","createTime":"2020-07-30T09:35:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T03:33:41.000Z","uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"535c50f086e474c9bde3ea3b395f7059bcfff94b","tid":2132252,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:35:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/8/88/NewClownGodcopy.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/340?cb=20060825124231\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F8%2F88%2FNewClownGodcopy.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%2Fscale-to-width-down%2F340%3Fcb%3D20060825124231&h=7b8a8968&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我信唯一的《基本法》，全能的人大，天地萬物，無論有形無形，都是祂所創造的。<br />\n<br />\n我信唯一的聖書、《基本法》、人大的獨生子。祂在萬世之前，由人大所寫。祂是出自人大的真理，出自光明的光明，出自真人大的真人大。祂是人大所生，而非人大所造，與人大同性同體，萬物是藉著祂而造成的。祂為了我們人類，並為了我們的得救，由北京頒下。祂因人大由童貞林鄭月娥取得肉軀，而成為人。祂在習近平執政時，為我們被釘在十字架上，受難而被埋葬。祂正如聖經所載，第三日復活了。祂升了天，放在人大的右邊。祂還要光榮地降來，審判參選人，祂的神國萬世無疆。<br />\n<br />\n我信《基本法》，祂是主及賦予生命者，由人大與林鄭月娥所共發。祂和人大與林鄭月娥，同受欽崇，同享光榮，祂曾藉選舉主任們發言。<br />\n<br />\n我信唯一、至聖、至公、從宗徒傳下來的特區政府。<br />\n<br />\n我承認赦罪的聖洗，只有一個。<br />\n<br />\n我期待死人的復活，及來世的生命。<br />\n<br />\n阿們。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa3635c79ed162fd3c9e2de8b5d8d8f7c94a238b","tid":2132252,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:40:37.000Z","msg":"正想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港依家政教合一<br />\n奉行基本法教"},{"pid":"40a2707888682c1a2d667b58f8176cc7ab61b881","tid":2132252,"uid":292267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:45:16.000Z","msg":"用呢篇野做政綱 報名參選 睇佢點"},{"pid":"bc24fa8a309b1b8ebd56102bb4ef810d9630cd8d","tid":2132252,"uid":250291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:48:03.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/116345327_2597553273892798_2284525329413212301_o.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_sid=9267fe&amp;_nc_ohc=KJK7gvgD3IAAX8Pc1VF&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;oh=7c3ac0f1488c891e33d685350c2e0d35&amp;oe=5F471CD6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih